item.title: 2021 in Review
item.description: 2021 was a wild year. Year two of our global pandemic. Like all years in recent memory, so much happened. January 6th, Among Us, Myanmar, Ever Given, Squid Game, NASA’s Ingenuity, Dune, James Webb Space Telescope. For me, it was a year of transition. I spent my entire high school senior year online and was itching to go in person to university knowing all of the risks. Even with all the changes, I had a great time during my first semester at UT and have come to love Austin as a city.
